/icon-62","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`set(icons)`**: Synchronously add icons to the store"},"435":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-63","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`ondemand(loader)`**: Register an asynchronous icon loader (returns unregister function)"},"436":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-64","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`parser(svgString)`**: Parse SVG strings into React elements"},"437":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-65","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"These are re-exports of the underlying Bento Icon system methods. For complete API documentation, advanced usage patterns, and implementation details, see the `@bento/icon` and `@bento/svg-parser` package documentation."},"438":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-66","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons integrate seamlessly with all Icon component features (transformations, accessibility, sprite mode, etc.)"},"439":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-67","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Multiple `ondemand` loaders can be registered and will be called in order until one returns content"},"440":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-68","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Use the `parser` function to convert SVG strings to React elements"},"441":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-69","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons are cached automatically just like CDN icons"},"442":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-70","page