rop is set (90, 180, or 270)"},"451":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-79","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"The component also includes accessibility attributes:"},"452":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-80","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`role=\"presentation\"`: For decorative icons"},"453":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-81","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`role=\"img\"`: When title prop is provided"},"454":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-82","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`focusable=\"false\"`: Prevents keyboard focus"},"455":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-83","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#inherit-from-parent-default","content":"By default, icons inherit the color from their parent element via `currentColor`:"},"456":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-84","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#explicit-colors","content":"Override the color with specific values:"},"457":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-85","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-transformations","content":"Transform capabilities are inherited from the Bento Illustration component. For complete transformation options and implementation details, see the `@bento/illustration` package documentation."},"458":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-86","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#rotation","content":"Rotate icons by 90-degree increments:"},"459":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-87","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#flipping","content":"Flip icons horizontally or vertically:"},"460":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-88","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#placeholder-content","content":"Provide fallback SVG content while icons load from the CDN:"},"461":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-89","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#decorative-icons","content":"For purely decorative icons, no additional attributes are needed. The icon will have `role=\"presentation\"` and be ignored by screen readers:"},"462":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-90","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#semantic-icons","content":"For icons that convey meaning, use the `title` prop. This automatically adds `role=\"img\"` and provides screen reader accessible text:"},"463":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-91","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#interactive-icons","content":"For interactive icons within buttons or links, use the `title` prop on the icon and `aria-label` on the interactive element:"},"464":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-92","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"Icons are loaded on-demand from a CDN using the following process:"},"465":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-93","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**First Request**: When an icon is first encountered, it triggers an asynchronous fetch from the CDN"},"466":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-94","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"},"467":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-95","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-ic