"],[356,"**`FieldError`** — surfaces the field's validation messages when it is invalid, and nothing when valid (a thin wrapper over React Aria `FieldError`)."],[350,"**`FieldGroup`** — the bordered box that visually unites a field's controls and reflects their shared focus, disabled, and invalid state. Used only by \"boxed\" fields (TextField, NumberField, Select, DateField); presentationally it is a React Aria `Group`."],[351,"**`FieldInput`** — the single-line control the user types into (a normalized React Aria `Input` given antares spacing via `Box`)."],[349,"**`FieldLabel`** — names the field and flags whether it's required (wraps React Aria `Label`, rendering an optional `*` indicator)."],[352,"**`FieldTextArea`** — the multiline control the user types into (a normalized React Aria `TextArea` given antares spacing via `Box`)."],[354,"**`FieldTrigger`** — a full-width value-display button inside the box that opens an overlay (used by Select and DatePicker): a value area plus a trailing icon, laid out across the group. `variant=\"select\"` is transparent and input-like; `variant=\"control\"` is a filled segment inside a shared group."],[428,"**`icon.content`**: Overrides the BentoIllustration component - affects SVG transformations (rotate, flip), accessibility attributes (`role`, `focusable`, `aria-labelledby`), viewBox calculations, and final SVG element rendering"],[427,"**`icon`**: Overrides the entire BentoIcon component - affects icon loading, caching, sprite/SVG mode switching, data attributes, and the overall icon wrapper"],[435,"**`ondemand(loader)`**: Register an asynchronous icon loader (returns unregister function)"],[436,"**`parser(svgString)`**: Parse SVG strings into React elements"],[434,"**`set(icons)`**: Synchronously add icons to the store"],[785,"**A step isn't clickable:** it has no `onPress`, so it's inert by design. Add `onPress` to make it interactive."],[415,"**Accessibility ready**: Built-in support for screen readers and keyboard navi